 The  consists of a collection of  objects.
 Each  represents a single array with a collection of attributes
 (see ) attached.
 If a provider works with large data sets, typically it doesn't loads all data in memory,
 but provides on-demand data access through variables.

 The following code iterates through all variables of a  
